{"tid":1653970,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"對準popo，一齊寫信拎cam片","createTime":"2019-10-14T10:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T14:06:54.000Z","uid":277194,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ed20c1fac8466380ea51c6e4be4075b024890b3a","tid":1653970,"uid":277194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T10:34:22.000Z","msg":"關於私隱條例，覺得有幾點大家要知道多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">私隱條例唔關心已經過世嘅人，所以就算公開相關CCTV，係無私隱問題</span></strong>（所以HKDI公開cctv係唔會開先例比popo任拎cctv嘅）<br />\n2. 理論上警方截查你嗰陣拎住支cam影你，你事後係可以引用私隱條例要求佢40日內提供副本<br />\n3. 雖然唔知狗牌號碼，但係有日期、時間、地點，除非當時有數以百計嘅cam同時錄緊，否則係可以trace到條片<br />\n4. Popo要先答你要求嘅嘢係咪真係有，然後就會要求你畀錢，作為佢預備副本嘅費用<br />\n5. Popo只能夠收成本價，嫌貴可以唔畀，或者向私隱專員公署投訴濫收<br />\n6. 條例以收到影片當日起計40日，如果收唔到條片，又可以去私隱專員公署投訴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正呀喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔衝唔緊要，人人都可以做雲海，大家約埋一齊submit、一齊countdown拎片！<br />\n溫馨提示：記得醒少少唔好自爆，寫信拎啲風平浪靜popo都影影影嗰啲。"},{"pid":"9f680ec7a7132f4f337961388a824a398279c128","tid":1653970,"uid":158546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T10:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a3f4f30d4ff7840c82c78fda69a84b96f78049","tid":1653970,"uid":319181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:06:54.000Z","msg":"唔止謝sir，連er er er sir都&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}